{"word":"H6923 - קָדַם - qâdam - kaw-dam' - Come before","slug":"H6923","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָדַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâdam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-dam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come before"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D3;&#x05DD; - qa&#x0302;dam</b> - <i>kaw-dam'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>project</i> (one self), that is, <i>precede</i>; hence to <i>anticipate</i>, <i>hasten</i>, <i>meet</i> (usually for help): - come (go, [flee]) before, + disappoint, meet, prevent."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6917\">H6917</a>, <a href=\"#/H6921\">H6921</a>, <a href=\"#/H6924\">H6924</a>, <a href=\"#/H6926\">H6926</a>, <a href=\"#/H6927\">H6927</a>, <a href=\"#/H6929\">H6929</a>, <a href=\"#/H6930\">H6930</a>, <a href=\"#/H6931\">H6931</a>, <a href=\"#/H6932\">H6932</a>, <a href=\"#/H6934\">H6934</a>, <a href=\"#/H6935\">H6935</a>"}]}